AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Potential Power
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT [Potential Power] FROM PowerCurve WHERE INTERPOLATE([Wind Speed], @[Adjusted Wind Speed;UOM=m/s])

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: WindSpeed := '{09cf446e-4c51-4b4f-9d40-f6ddfd26715e};Adjusted Wind Speed'; ApPw := 0.1892*WindSpeed^5 - 7.374*WindSpeed^4 + 102.85*WindSpeed^3 - 615.26*WindSpeed^2 + 1665.4*WindSpeed - 1684.4; VarCutOut := if (WindSpeed > 25) then 20 else ( if (WindSpeed < 20) then 25 else ( if (PrevVal('{8c606aa4-2c42-4efd-bcff-b0ad36ebdc6c};CutOut', '*') = 20) then 20 else 25 ) ); ApparentPw := if (WindSpeed < 3.5 Or WindSpeed > VarCutOut Or '{68d41ed4-5efa-447a-8514-9d1b20002ba4};Status' <> "Run") then 0 Else (if (WindSpeed > 11) then 3000 Else ApPw); ApPwAvg := ( ApparentPw + ( if(BadVal(TagVal('{31494947-b565-45a0-8d13-dab2f98fa164};Apparent Power','*-90s'))) then 0 else TagVal('{31494947-b565-45a0-8d13-dab2f98fa164};Apparent Power','*-90s') ) + ( if(BadVal(TagVal('{31494947-b565-45a0-8d13-dab2f98fa164};Apparent Power','*-60s'))) then 0 else TagVal('{31494947-b565-45a0-8d13-dab2f98fa164};Apparent Power','*-60s') ) + ( if(BadVal(TagVal('{31494947-b565-45a0-8d13-dab2f98fa164};Apparent Power','*-30s'))) then 0 else TagVal('{31494947-b565-45a0-8d13-dab2f98fa164};Apparent Power','*-30s') ) )/4; AcPw := Abs(ApPwAvg*'{0dab5856-0ff1-4efd-97aa-2c621f2034b7};Power Factor');

Variable1 := (Hour('*') * 60 + Minute('*') + 0) Mod 5; Variable2 := (Hour('*') * 60 + Minute('*') + 1) Mod 5; Variable3 := (Hour('*') * 60 + Minute('*') + 2) Mod 5; Variable4 := (Hour('*') * 60 + Minute('*') + 3) Mod 5; Variable5 := (Hour('*') * 60 + Minute('*') + 4) Mod 5;
A := Rand(1,0.08); Variable1 := If A>1 Then A-2 Else A;

Variable1 := Rand(5,10); Variable2 := If Variable1 <= 8 Then 0 Else (if Variable1 > 8 And Variable1 <= 9 Then 1 else 2); Variable4 := If Variable2=0 Then 0 Else Trunc(Rand(5,8)); Variable3 := If Variable4<>1 Then 0 Else Trunc(Rand(3.5,5));
TurbAWS := '..|Wind Speed'*Rand(1,0.2); Variable1 := If '..|Wind Speed'<20 And TurbAWS>=20 Then 19.99-Rand(0.1,0.1) Else If '..|Wind Speed'>=20 And TurbAWS<20 Then 20.01+Rand(0.1,0.1) Else TurbAWS;
